you smeller
says the ceo of stinkyville central
those are some bold words coming from the lord of smellerton
I darest thou to speak these words to my face monseiur stench. your reputation preceeds you on account of the ungovernable fragrance you carry. thou art better suited to dine with an ass than in the company of someone with such distinguished presence as myself. shame upon you sir and your complete family tree for this outrageous accusation. in addition to these things i have also had intimite affairs with the woman who birthed you.